rComments: This Prof worked with me personally making me feel like less of a number and more like a human student. Without his support I would not have passed this course. He is incredibly nice and caring.

Passionate about his field, extremely friendly. He really wants the best for his students and makes math that much less intimidating. Being a life sci student, he enable me to really enjoy math for what it is and his enthusiasm is contagious.
Great guy. Makes some lame but funny jokes during class which keep it kind of interesting.
Amazing prof. he managed to make a 3hr calculus class enjoyable. You could really tell he put a lot of preparation into his lectures.
Mr. Eagle is a nice guy, however, his hand writing and notes is so unorganized. I'd say that as long as u do the problems in the textbook you'll be fine.
